<|ref|>equation<|/ref|><|det|>[[401, 400, 870, 427]]<|/det|>
\[\beta = 1.2\eta_{\mathrm{e}}\left(T_{\mathrm{gm}} / T_{1}\right)^{\gamma} \quad (L.1.1-1)\]  

